></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8421951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8421951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 01, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qjw1727679366123.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qjw1727679366123.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qjw1727679366123.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qjw1727679366123\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">cert.exe</code> executable is used to certify Uniface applications and\n\t\tfacilitates the creation of public/private key pairs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">cert.exe {-key} | {-certify ResourceDir/UAR PrivateKey}</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Switches</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Option</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-key</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__2\">Creates a private/public key pairs.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-certify ResourceDir/UAR PrivateKey</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"qjw1727679366123__table_mjm_yjx_wcc__entry__2\">Certifies the target Uniface application. You need to specify the Resource directory,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tor the UAR you want to certify, and the PrivateKey.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__section_kl2_zjx_wcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d887663e107\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Cert is created to protect your database connections, as well as the integrity of\n\t\t\t\tyour application against malicious third parties.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__note_zks_13y_wcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<p class=\"p\">It is available on Windows only.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__section_wp5_1kx_wcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d887663e122\">Generating Private/Public key pairs</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">You can generate key pairs with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">cert.exe -key</code> option. You can\n\t\t\t\talso generate them with other tools, as long as they follow the specifications we\n\t\t\t\thave set.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information about generating keys with OpenSSL, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"afq1727770776688.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afq1727770776688.html\" title=\"Procedure to certify a Uniface application.\">How to Certify a Uniface Application</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qjw1727679366123__section_igl_zkx_wcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d887663e145\">Certifying Uniface applications</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">To certify an entire directory or a UAR, using your private key, simply specify them\n\t\t\t\tas shown in the table above.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">When using a private key generated by third party tools, make sure it follows the\n\t\t\t\tspecifications we have set for those keys.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">When specifying a directory instead of a UAR, make sure that the directory follows the Uniface\n\t\t\t\tresource structure, as in the directory you specified in\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">$RESOURCES_OUTPUT</code>. You cannot specify a sub-folder. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdx1727679205591.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdx1727679205591.html\" title=\"Certifying a deployed Uniface application can safeguard the privacy of your data. This functionality helps you to verify the validity of your application during runtime, making sure that your database connection settings cannot be used with unauthorized applications.\">Certifying Uniface Applications</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdx1727679205591.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Certifying Uniface Applications</a><p>Certifying a deployed Uniface application can safeguard the privacy of your data. This functionality helps you to verify the validity of your application during runtime, making sure that your database connection settings cannot be used with unauthorized applications.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421951\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "cert.exe Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 01, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The cert.exe executable is used to certify Uniface applications and facilitates the creation of public/private key pairs. cert.exe {-key} | {-certify ResourceDir/UAR PrivateKey} Switches Option Description -key Creates a private/public key pairs. -certify ResourceDir/UAR PrivateKey Certifies the target Uniface application. You need to specify the Resource directory, or the UAR you want to certify, and the PrivateKey. Description Cert is created to protect your database connections, as well as the integrity of your application against malicious third parties. Note: It is available on Windows only. Generating Private/Public key pairs You can generate key pairs with the cert.exe -key option. You can also generate them with other tools, as long as they follow the specifications we have set. For more information about generating keys with OpenSSL, see How to Certify a Uniface Application . Certifying Uniface applications To certify an entire directory or a UAR, using your private key, simply specify them as shown in the table above. When using a private key generated by third party tools, make sure it follows the specifications we have set for those keys. When specifying a directory instead of a UAR, make sure that the directory follows the Uniface resource structure, as in the directory you specified in $RESOURCES_OUTPUT . You cannot specify a sub-folder. For more information, see Certifying Uniface Applications . Related Links Certifying Uniface Applications Certifying a deployed Uniface application can safeguard the privacy of your data. This functionality helps you to verify the validity of your application during runtime, making sure that your database connection settings cannot be used with unauthorized applications. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}